headline: Skild AI Accelerates Development of Human-like Robot Brain with AI Solutions from Hewlett Packard Enterprise
summary: HOUSTON, March 13, 2025--Skild AI, a company creating AI foundation models and software designed to drive a diverse range of robotic devices and applications, is powering an exponential expansion of its engineering operations with a secure, private AI-as-a-service solution by STN comprising AI servers and storage solutions from Hewlett Packard Enterprise (NYSE: HPE). The deployment will advance Skild AI’s development of artificial general intelligence (AGI) rooted in the physical world.
